  "texts": [
    "It was studied and computed in [190].• Assumptions about the medium (degrees of freedom, etc.",
    ")We assume the accuracy of the one-gluon exchange approximation and HTLs.",
    "The only exception is the real part of the potential in the lattice-inspired scenario, which is taken from a fit to lattice data.",
    "• Temperature dependence of heavy quark masses Our heavy quark masses do not depend on temperature.",
    "• Equilibrium limits in transport Strictly speaking, the equations we use do not bring the system to equilibrium because we did not include regeneration."
